                        <msItem xml:id="p2_i1">
                        <locus from="73" to="86v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4065Prayer">Prayer of thanksgiving for the offering of the incense</title>
                        <listBibl type="secondary">
                           <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/8UWD3FCM"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Petrus1548Test"/><title level="m">Testamentum Novum: Cum Epistola Pauli Ad Hebreos tantum, cum concordantijs Evangelistarum Eusebii &amp; numeratione omnium verborum eorundem. Missale cum benedictione incensi cerae et c. Alphabetum in lingua ግእዝ፡ gheez, idest libera quia a nulla alia originem duxit, &amp; vulgo dicitur Chaldea, Quae omnia Fr. Petrus Ethyops auxilio piorum sedente Paulo. III. Pont. MAx. &amp; Claudio illius regni Imperatore imprimi curavit</title><author><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Petrus Ethyops</t:name></author><pubPlace>Romae</pubPlace><publisher>Impensis Petri Comos Ethiopis, Valerius Doricus</publisher><date>1548</date><note type="url">https://books.google.de/books?id=KPNa9Mc5gjYC</note><citedRange unit="page">174ra l. 9 - f. 176vb l. 13</citedRange></bibl>
                        </listBibl>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ወእምዝ፡ ይጼሊ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ጸሎተ፡ አኰቴት፡ ወያዐርግ፡ 
                        
                              <sic>ዕጣን፡</sic>
                            እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ተወከፍ፡ እምኔየ፡ እግዚኦ፡ አነ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ዘንተ፡ ንጹሐ፡ ዕጣነ፡ ለስርየተ፡ ኃጢአትየ፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ሕዝብከ፡ አሜን፨ = ፨ 
                        ወእምዝ፡ 
                              <sic>የዓርግ፡</sic>
                            ቀሲስ፡ ዕጣነ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ንስእለከ፡ ወናስተበቍዓከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ አምላክነ፨ በከመ፡ ሠመርከ፡ ቍርባነ፡ አቤል፡ 
                     
                              <sic>ፍቁረከ፨</sic>
                            መሥዋዕተ፡ ሄኖክ፡ ወኖኅ፡ ወአብርሃም፨ ወዕጣነ፡ አሮን፡ ወሳሙኤል፡ ወዘካርያስ፨
                     </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        በእግዚአብሔር፡ ስምከ፡ ዘእምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ በአማኑኤል፡ ስምከ፡ ዘኢይትመዋ<supplied reason="omitted">እ</supplied>፡ ለፀር፡ በኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ስምከ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ አነ፡ 
                        ገብርከ፨ እገሌ፨ እምይእዜ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                     </msItem>
                  
                        <msItem xml:id="p2_i2">
                        <locus from="86v" to="98"/>
                        <title>Litanies</title>
                     
                           <msItem xml:id="p2_i2.1">
                           <locus from="86v"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1807Litonz">Liṭon za-nagh</title>
                           <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           ሰራዬ፡ ኩን፡ ለነ፡ ወኢትሕድገነ፡ ሃብ፡ ሞገሰ፡ ንርከብ፡ በቅድሜከ፡ ወበቅድመ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልድከ፨ ዘቦቱ፡ ለከ፡ ምስሌሁ፡ ወምስለ፡ ቅዱስ፡ መንፈስ፡ ስብሐት፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                           </explicit>
                        </msItem>
                     
                           <msItem xml:id="p2_i2.2">
                           <locus from="87v"/>
                              <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4858Litany">ሊጦን፡</title>
                           <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                         ስምከ፡ ሕያው፡ ዘኢይመውት፡ ትጉህ፡ ዘኢይዴቅስ፡ 
                                 <sic>ፈጣሬ፡</sic>
                               ዘኢይደክም።
                        </explicit>
                        </msItem>
                     
                           <msItem xml:id="p2_i2.3">
                           <locus from="88v"/>
                              <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4711Mastabqwe">Prayers for the sick, the pilgrims, the rain, the fruits of the earth, the water of the rivers, the king, the offerers, the sleepers, the catechumens, the peace</title>
                           <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                          ሀብ፡ 
                                 <sic>ምክር፡</sic>
                               ለመኳንንተ፡ አሕዛብ፡ አግዋርነ፡ በአተነ፡ ወጸአተነ፡ በኵሉ፡ ሰላም፡ ዕቀበነ፡ ከመ፡ በህዱእ፡ ወበጽምው፡ ሕይወተ፡ 
                           እንዘ፡ ነሐዩ፡ በኵሉ፡ አምልኮተ፡ ሠናይ፡ 
                                 <sic>ወኂሩተ፡ </sic>
                               ንትረከብ፡ በክርስቶስ፡ በ፩ወልድከ፡ ዘቦዩ፨ 
                        </explicit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                  
                        <msItem xml:id="p2_i3">
                           <locus from="98" to="106"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1716Kidanz">ኪዳን፡</title>
                        </msItem>
                           
                           <msItem xml:id="p2_i4">
                              <locus from="106" to="132"/>
                              <title>Ordinary of the mass and Anaphora of the Apostles</title>
                              <msItem xml:id="p2_i4.1">
                                 <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#SerataQeddase">Ordinary of the mass</title>
                              </msItem>
                              <msItem xml:id="p2_i4.2">
