                              </msItem>          
                           </msItem>
                           
                        <msItem xml:id="p2_i5">
                           <locus from="132" to="140"/>
                           <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእነ፡</title>
                           <msItem xml:id="p2_i5.1">
                           <locus from="138v" to="140"/>
                              <title>Explanation of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps94"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps94</span></ref>
                           </title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        እስመ፡ ከመዝ፡ ይቤ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮም፡ ለእመ፡ ሰማዕክሙ፡ 
                                 <sic>ቃሉ፡</sic>
                               ኢታጽ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ዑ፡  <sic>ልብ<supplied reason="omitted">ክ</supplied>ሙ፡</sic>
                               ...  ዑቁ፡ እንከ፡ አኃዊነ፡ ወኢይትረከብ፡ በላዕለ፡ ፩እምኔክሙ፡ ልበ፡ እኩይ፡ 
                        ወሕፁጸ፡ ሃይማኖት፡
                     </incipit>
                           <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                      ከመዝ፡ ይቤ፡ በእንተ፡ ሰንበት፡ ወአዕረፈ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በዕለተ፡ ሰንበት፡ እምኵሉ፡ ግብሩ፨
                     </explicit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                  
