                           <handDesc>
                              <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">
                                 <ab type="script"/>
                                 <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>
                                 <date/>
                                 <desc> The handwriting retains old paleographic features: 
                                    ሎ has the loop marking the 7th order attached directly to the body of the letter, without the linking line; 
                                    መ and ሠ have angular loops; 
                                    the upper part of some letters, e.g. ቆ, ቶ, ኖ, የ, ደ, ጸ, has a triangular shape; 
                                    the left stroke of ዘ is slightly slanted.
                                 </desc>
                                 <seg type="rubrication"/>
                              </handNote>
                           </handDesc>
                           
                           <additions>
                              <list>
                                 <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">Ownership note</desc>
                                    <locus target="#143r"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                       ፪፻፡ ፳ወ፫፡ ማዕ፡ ሬስ፡ ፪፻፡ ሳን፡ ፫፡ ፻፡ ታው፡ ፬፻፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ 
                                    <sic>ዘማዕቀባ፡</sic>
                                  እግዚእ፡ ወልደ፡ ቢዘን፡ ወልደ፡ ፊልጶስ፡ ዘሄዳ፡ ወዘሰረቃ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ወውቁይ፡ ይኩን፡ በአፈ፡ አብ።ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ። አሜን። 
                                    </q>
                                    <note>The note contains an explanation of the numeric value of four Hebrew letters. It also states that the book belongs to 
                                       <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11262MaqabaE">Māʿqabā ʾƎgziʾ</persName> of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2252DabraB">(Dabra) Bizan</placeName>, 
                                       who was a <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11263HouseFil">spiritual son of Filǝṗṗos</persName>.
                                    </note>
                                 </item>
                                 
                                 <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <desc type="CalendaricNote"/>
                                    <locus from="143v" to="144r"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                       <choice>
                                    <sic>ወበዘንዜክር፡</sic>
                                
                                 <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ወበዘንዜከር፡</corr>  </choice>
                                
                                    <sic>ሐሰበ፡</sic>
                                 
                                       በመዋዕለ፡ ማቴዎስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ በ፷፻፡ ወ፭፻፡ ፷ወ፱፡ ዐመተ፡ ምኅረት፡ ፯ለጥምቀት፡ መጥቅዕ፡ ፲ወ፯፡ ለጥቅምት፡ ፲ወ፰፡ 
                                    <sic>ለምያዝያ፡</sic>
                                  ትንሳኤ፡ ፲ወ፪፡ 
                                       <del rend="erasure">ለምያዝያ፡</del> 
                                 
                                    <sic>ለገንቦት፡</sic>
                                  ረክብ፡ ፳ወ፮፡ ለግንቦት፡ ዕርገት፡ እምሰብዑ፡ ለሰኔ፡ ርደተ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘ፳ወ፭፡ 
                                    <sic>ስርቀ፡</sic>
                                  ሌሊት፡ ፩መአልት፡
                                    </q>
                                    <note>The note indicates the days of the moveable feasts of the year of mercy <date>6569</date>, year of Matthew.</note>
                                 </item>
                              </list>
